item.description: This was sort of a last minute decision on my part. As it may rain on Sunday I am scheduling this for tomorrow if any one cares to join me. It will probably take about 2 hours. There will be some hilly parts so with the snow you might want to bring (a) hiking pole(s) to help steady your selves. If you end up getting there late I will be hitting the trails at 11:10 AM. We can wait under the power lines once we get there until it is time to start.
